pan style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">企</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">業</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">建</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">設</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">進</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">程，推</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">動</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">在</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">產</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">礦</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">山</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">企</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">業</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">穩</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">產</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">增</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">產，通</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">過</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">強</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">化</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">管</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">理</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">實</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">現</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">提</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">質</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">增</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">效，</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">全</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">面</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">提</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">升</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">經</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">營</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">效</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">率</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">和</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">盈</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">利</span><span style=\"font-size-ignore:13pt;\">能</span><span style=\"font-size